summary: Simple Ancient Nord with Yngol helm skins and powerful Berserker enchantments!
descriptionHtml:
Heavy armor, Ancient Nord skins and Yngol helm skin. Includes a battleaxe, Nord Hero skin.
Already enchanted, temperable, and craftable. Great for a berserker!

The Warhelm's -20% Shout timer makes Shouts have no CD for some reason. It might end up looking like -200 second cooldown or something ridiculous like that. I'm not sure how to fix it, but I'm sure it's just that enchantment.

The armour's quality is Dragonplate, and the battleaxe's quality is Dragonbone. Also, the axe absorbs Stamina instead of health now.

------------------------------------------------------

I added a new version including a greatsword and ring, and tweaked the enchantment on the helmet.

------------------------------------------------------

Guys, I will not be working on this mod anymore, nor do I really think it needs much more work. When I got my new computer, I lost the original file, and I do not feel like remaking this from scratch. If I ever do, I'll update and let you guys know.

------------------------------------------------------

*NEW*
